pytest finds test_login_page.py and test_pim_page.py
it imports conftest.py, tests/..., pages/..., utilities/...
ReadConfig loads config.ini
pd.read_excel() loads test data from Excel
logger() fixture is created once and returns the logger
driver() fixture starts Chrome once
each test method is called with driver and logger injected
page objects are created with LoginPage(driver) or PIMPage(driver)
BasePage methods handle Selenium waits and actions, logging each step
if a step fails, an exception is raised and pytest marks the test failed
after all tests, driver.quit() closes Chrome